== 地質 ==
針山山體由針山花崗岩構成。酸性岩漿在[[白堊紀|白堊紀]]形時入侵地殼，於城門河谷的西北方形成一個東北-西南走向的侵入體。岩漿冷卻後結晶成呈淡粉紅灰色、細粒及部份具斑狀岩理的針山花崗岩<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E9%80%9A%E8%AD%98%E5%B0%8E%E8%B3%9E%EF%B9%95%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%9C%89%E7%A4%A6%E6%8E%A1/web_tc/article/20140525/s00005/1400954255498|title=通識導賞﹕香港有礦採|publisher=明報|author=蔡琇莹|date=2014-05-25|accessdate=2018-01-20|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2018-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180120124300/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E9%80%9A%E8%AD%98%E5%B0%8E%E8%B3%9E%EF%B9%95%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%9C%89%E7%A4%A6%E6%8E%A1/web_tc/article/20140525/s00005/1400954255498|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於較圍岩抗蝕，經剝蝕後突起成為針山。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://hkss.cedd.gov.hk/hkss/eng/education/GS/tc/hkg/chapter6.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-04-06 |archive-date=2019-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911112802/http://hkss.cedd.gov.hk/hkss/eng/education/GS/tc/hkg/chapter6.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>
